      "text": "Kur irr waj? kur irr Wat-\ndi? kur irr Bahrschana? kur irr\nSchehloschanas? kur irr Wahtes\nbes Wainas? kur irr farkanns\nAzzis?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pee teem/ kas pee Wiḣ-\nna katwejahs/ pee teem/ kas nahk\npamaischu Dsehreenu mekleht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ne luhko pehz ta Wiḣna/\nka tas tik farkans irr/ ka wiꞥſch\nBikkeri tik jauks raugahs:\nWiꞥſch gan gluddeni ee-eet/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet pehz kohsch tas ka\nTschuhfka/ un duṙr ka Ohdfe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad taiwas Azzis pehz\nfwefschahm Seewahm skattifees/\nun tawa Sirds runnahs pahr-\nwehrtitas Leetas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tu buhſt ka weens/\nkas Juhraś Widdû gull/ un ka\nweens/ kas Mastas Wirś Gal-\nlā gull.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es tohpu fifsē/ bet tas\nman ne fahp/ es tohpu kulfs/ bet\nes to ne juhtu. Rad es jelle us-\nmohdischohs/ ka es utkaṙ to pa-\nschu dsennu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XXIV. Nodalla.\nMahza/ ka buhs pazeeťgam mestees/ un preeffch\nwiṣadas Besdeeшибas fargatees/ nedś us to\nBesdeewigо Laimi standeht / bet Deewa\nWahrdụ mihleht/ kas Swchtumu dohd/ un\nzerreht / ka tomehr kahdi Augti no tahs\nDeewabihjafchanas nahkfseez : 1. etc. Mah-\nza arridsan/ ka buhs eekch tahdas Pazee-\nchanas pastahwigam palikt: 23.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "E bahrgojecs pahr nik-\nneem Zilwekeem/ ne ee-\nkahrojees arridsan pee\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo winnu Sirds dohm-\nus Pohstschanu/ un winnu Luḣ-\npas runna no Nelaimibas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zaur Gudribu tohp ta-\nNams uzelts/ un zaur Sa-\npraschanu stiprinahts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un zaur Samanu toh-\ntee Kambart peepilditi/ ar wiḣ-\ndu dahrgu un peemihligu Bag-\ngatibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Gudrs Wihrs irr spehzigs\nun tas Wihrs/ kam Sinnafscha-\nna irr/ tas irr fohti warre-\nstiprs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo zaur prahtigeem Pa-\ndohmeim warri tu karroht / u-\nkur dauds Padohma-Deweju\nirr/ tur irr Uswarrefchana.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tan Geffim irr ta Gu-\nriba weena wiḣai augsta Leeta-\nwiꞥſch jawu Mutti ne drihg-\natdarriht Wahrtis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas pahrdohma Lann-\ndarriht/ tas pats jatauz Blehd-\npahr wiﬀeem Blehscheem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta Geffa Dohmas i-\nGreksi/ un weens Mehdtajs i-\nZilwekeem weena Negantiba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja tu Behdu Deend ni-\ngursti/ tad tew ne irr dau-\nSpehka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Isglahb tohs/ kas u-\nNokaufchanu irr fazemti/ w-\ntad tu gribbetu atrantees-\nteem/ kas pee Nomahkchan-\ntohp westi?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja tu fakki: Redsi/ me-\nto ne prohtam/ neggi tas/ k-\nSirdis pahrmanua / to ni-\npro\n"
    }
